Pitch:
Descend a hive of varying insects to kill the queen.
Possibly has to return to the surface portal to escape.
Collecting honey might increase score reward (though honey is also a healing item).

Player:
Possibly a sentient ant-bear (or other insect eating species).

Combat:
Melee, ranged & item focused.
Some actions usually passive in roguelikes are active toggles.
No magic, possibly skill system for player.

Dungeon:
Initial levels are a cellar (filled with equipment racks etc.), descending into the hive makes loot rarer.

Enemies:
Various insects, distinct attack patterns/AI (e.g. Bee lancer: charges from distance, then keeps distance again).